<HL>
   Northrop Wins Air Force Pact
</HL>
<DATE>
08/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C15
</SO>
<CO>
   NOC TRW CMIC HPH
</CO>
<GV>
DEFENSE DEPARTMENT (DEF)
</GV>
<LP>
   WASHINGTON -- Northrop Corp. received a $35.4 million Air
Force contract for support of undergraduate pilot training.
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   TRW Corp. received a $30.9 million Air Force contract for
improvements to the Cheyenne Mountain complex.
                                                                                                       

   California Microwave Inc. got a $17.8 million Army
contract for a classified system.
                                                                                                       

   Institute for Defense Analysis was awarded a $10 million
Army contract for defense studies.
</TEXT>
